This is a readme for the repo that hosts my vimfiles.

Quick setup: 
1. git clone https://github.com/quanticle/vimfiles.git
2. cd vimfiles
3. git submodule init
4. git submodule update
5. (On Linux) ln -s vimrc ~/.vimrc

To add a new Pathogen bundle: 
  git submodule add <bundle repo> bundle/<name of bundle>
  git submodule init bundle/<name of bundle>

To remove a Pathogen bundle:
  git submodule deinit bundle/<name of bundle>
  Remove the corresponding entries in .gitmodules
